endip.help: Final IPv4 address (inclusive) in the range of the addresses to be translated (format xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx, default: 0.0.0.0).
endip.name: endip

map-startip.help: Address to be used as the starting point for translation in the range (format xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx, default: 0.0.0.0).
map-startip.name: map-startip

startip.help: First IPv4 address (inclusive) in the range of the addresses to be translated (format xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx, default: 0.0.0.0).
startip.name: startip
